				SwiftStack Nodes is an integrated stack to enable an operator to 
get up and running quickly. Once installed, a SwiftStack Node connects 
to the SwiftStack Controller, where it receives its configuration.
			</p>
			<h3>
				SwiftStack Nodes:
			</h3>
			<ul class="list">
				<li>
