			<h1>
				SwiftStack Controller
			</h1>
			<p>
				The SwiftStack Controller manages SwiftStack nodes from initial 
deployment to production. The SwiftStack Controller automatically 
configures and deploys availability zones based on hardware topology and
 preferences. The SwiftStack Nodes are instrumented to provide 
diagnostic monitoring data to the Controller, which significantly 
shortens the time to resolve potential bottlenecks and hardware 
failures.  
     The SwiftStack controller is <a href="http://www.swiftstack.com/product/controller">provided two ways: in the cloud or on-premise</a>.
